\c 4
\nb
\v 1 UMozisi wasephendula wathi: Kodwa khangela, kabayikungikholwa, kabayikulilalela ilizwi lami; ngoba bazakuthi: IN\nd kosi\nd* kayibonakalanga kuwe.
\v 2 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Kuyini lokho okusesandleni sakho? Wasesithi: Yintonga\x + 4.17,20.\x*.
\v 3 Yasisithi: Iphosele emhlabathini. Waseyiphosela emhlabathini, yasisiba yinyoka. UMozisi waseyibalekela.
\v 4 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Yelula isandla sakho, uyibambe ngomsila. Waselula isandla sakhe, wayithi xhaka; yasisiba yintonga esandleni sakhe,
\v 5 ukuze bakholwe\x + 19.9.\x* ukuthi ibonakele kuwe iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyise, uNkulunkulu kaAbrahama, uNkulunkulu kaIsaka, loNkulunkulu kaJakobe\x + 3.6.\x*.
\p
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi njalo kuye: Ake ufake isandla sakho esifubeni sakho. Wasesifaka isandla sakhe esifubeni sakhe; esesikhuphile, khangela-ke, isandla sakhe sasesilobulephero njengeliqhwa elikhithikileyo\x + Nani 12.10. 2 Kho. 5.27.\x*.
\v 7 Yasisithi: Buyisela isandla sakho esifubeni sakho. Wasesibuyisela isandla sakhe esifubeni sakhe; esesikhuphile esifubeni sakhe, khangela-ke, sasesiphenduke saba njengenyama yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 5.14.\x*.
\v 8 Njalo kuzakuthi uba bengakukholwa, bengalaleli ilizwi lesibonakaliso sokuqala, bazakholwa ilizwi lesibonakaliso sokucina.
\v 9 Kuzakuthi-ke, uba bengakholwa lalezizibonakaliso ezimbili, bengalaleli ilizwi lakho, uzakukha okwamanzi omfula, uwathele emhlabathini owomileyo; njalo kuzakuthi amanzi ozawakha emfuleni azakuba ligazi\x + 7.19.\x* emhlabathini owomileyo.
\p
\v 10 UMozisi wasesithi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni: Uxolo, Nkosi yami, kangisiso sikhulumi\f + \fk isikhulumi: \fl Heb. \fq indoda yamazwi.\f*, ngitsho kusukela endulo\f + \fk mandulo: \fl Heb. \fq izolo lakuthangi.\f*, ngitsho kusukela usukhulume lenceku yakho; ngoba kunzima emlonyeni wami njalo kunzima olimini\x + 6.12. Jer. 1.6.\x*.
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Ngubani owenzela umuntu umlomo? Kumbe ngubani owenza isimungulu, kumbe isacuthe, kumbe obonayo, kumbe isiphofu? Kakusimi yini iN\nd kosi\nd*?
\v 12 Khathesi-ke hamba, njalo mina ngizakuba lomlomo wakho, ngikufundise lokho ozakukhuluma\x + Isa. 50.4. Jer. 1.9. Mat. 10.19. Mark. 13.11. Luka 12.11,12; 21.14,15.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa wathi: Uxolo, Nkosi yami, akuthume ngesandla salowo ozamthuma\x + Jer. 51.3.\x*.
\v 14 Lwaseluvutha ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi, yasisithi: Angithi uAroni umLevi ngumnewenu? Ngiyazi ukuthi angakhuluma kuhle. Njalo khangela-ke, uzaphuma ukukuhlangabeza; nxa ekubona, uzathaba enhliziyweni yakhe.
\v 15 Njalo uzakhuluma kuye\x + 7.1,2.\x*, ufake amazwi emlonyeni wakhe\x + Nani 22.38; 23.5,12,16. 2 Sam. 14.3,19. Isa. 51.16.\x*; mina-ke ngizakuba lomlomo wakho lomlomo wakhe, ngizalifundisa lokho elizakwenza.
\v 16 Yena-ke uzakhuluma esizweni esikhundleni sakho, kuzakuthi abe ngumlomo kuwe, wena ube njengoNkulunkulu kuye\x + 7.1; 18.19.\x*.
\v 17 Njalo uzathatha lintonga esandleni sakho, ozakwenza izibonakaliso ngayo\x + 4.2; 7.15.\x*.
\s UMozisi ubuyela eGibhithe
\p
\v 18 UMozisi wasehamba wabuyela kuJetro uyisezala, wathi kuye: Ake ungiyekele ngihambe, ngibuyele kubafowethu abaseGibhithe, ngibone ukuthi basaphila yini. UJetro wasesithi kuMozisi: Hamba ngokuthula.
\v 19 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi eMidiyani: Hamba, ubuyele eGibhithe; ngoba wonke amadoda asafa, ayedinga umphefumulo wakho\x + 2.15,23. Mat. 2.20.\x*.
\v 20 UMozisi wasethatha umkakhe lamadodana akhe, wabakhwelisa phezu kukababhemi, wabuyela elizweni leGibhithe. UMozisi wasethatha intonga kaNkulunkulu esandleni sakhe\x + 17.9. Nani 20.8,9.\x*.
\v 21 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Ekuhambeni kwakho ubuyela eGibhithe, bona ukuthi, zonke izimangaliso\x + 3.20.\x* engizibeke esandleni sakho, uzenze phambi kukaFaro. Kodwa ngizakwenza inhliziyo yakhe ibe lukhuni\x + 7.3,13,14,22; 8.14,15; 9.12,35; 10.1; 14.8. Josh. 11.20. Dute. 2.30. Isa. 63.17. Roma 9.18.\x* ukuze angasiyekeli isizwe sihambe.
\v 22 Njalo uzakuthi kuFaro: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Indodana yami\x + Hos. 11.1.\x*, izibulo lami\x + Jer. 31.9.\x*, nguIsrayeli;
\v 23 njalo sengithe kuwe: Yekela indodana yami ihambe ukuthi ingikhonze; kodwa walile ukuyiyekela ihambe, khangela, ngizabulala indodana yakho, izibulo lakho\x + 11.5; 12.29.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Kwasekusithi esendleleni, endlini yezihambi\x + Gen. 42.27; 43.21.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* yahlangana laye\x + Nani 22.22. Gen. 17.14.\x*, yadinga ukumbulala.
\v 25 UZipora wasethatha insengetshe, waquma ijwabu laphambili lendodana yakhe, walithintisa inyawo zakhe wathi: Isibili ungumyeni wegazi kimi.
\v 26 Yasimyekela\x + Hlu. 11.37. Ngoma 3.4. Neh. 6.9.\x*. Ngalesosikhathi wathi: Umyeni wegazi, ngenxa yokusoka.
\p
\v 27 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuAroni: Hamba, uyehlangabeza uMozisi enkangala\x + 4.14.\x*. Wahamba-ke, wahlangana laye entabeni kaNkulunkulu\x + 3.1; 18.5. 1 Kho. 19.8.\x*, wamanga.
\v 28 UMozisi wasemtshela uAroni\x + 4.15,16.\x* wonke amazwi eN\nd kosi\nd* eyayimthumile, lazo zonke izibonakaliso eyayimlaye zona.
\p
\v 29 OMozisi loAroni basebehamba, babuthanisa bonke abadala babantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 3.16.\x*.
\v 30 UAroni wasekhuluma amazwi wonke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayiwakhulume kuMozisi\x + 4.16.\x*, wenza izibonakaliso phambi kwamehlo abantu.
\v 31 Abantu basebekholwa\x + 3.18. 4.8,9.\x*; bezwa ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* ihambele\x + 3.16.\x* abantwana bakoIsrayeli, lokuthi ibonile inhlupheko yabo\x + 2.25; 3.7.\x*, bakhothama, bakhonza\x + Gen. 24.26. Eks. 12.27. 1 Kho. 1.16,31. 1 Lan. 29.20.\x*.